Definition at line 15 of file CTracerCommands.h.

enum ilolv::CTracerCommands::TracerMode

Working mode of object tracer.

Enumerator:
TM_DISABLED  No action is supported.

Whole actions of object tracer are disabled.

TM_MANUAL  Manual mode.

Some actions like manual trigger can be made.

TM_AUTOMATIC  Automatic mode.

Objects will be traced, if there is no response from application they will be autonomic ejected.

TM_DIAGNOSTIC  Diagnostic mode.

Some special actions are possible.
